title: Fall of Raqqa: The secret deal - BBC News
description:
When US-backed Syrian fighters took full control of the city of Raqqa, it ended three years of rule there by so-called Islamic State. But now the BBC has uncovered details of a secret deal that let several hundred IS fighters escape. IS made Raqqa in northern Syria its headquarters in early 2014. Last month Raqqa fell, but this programme has learnt that in exchange for a deal to save lives and bring peace to the city, a convoy carrying several hundred IS fighters, their families and weapons and ammunition -- were able to leave the city freely. The question now is, where are they now? Our Middle East Correspondent, Quentin Sommerville, has this exclusive report.

tags: Germany|"vs"|"France"|"1-2"|"Highlights"|"Goals"|"14"|"November"|"2017"|"Germany vs France"|"Germany vs France 2017"|"Germany vs France 1-2"|"Germany France"|"Football"|"Minds"|"Lacazette"|"Deutschland"|"2x2"
description:
English Commentary
By FOOTBALL MINDS

Germany vs France 2-2 Highlights & Goals
14 November 2017.

0-1 Lacazette
1-1 Werner
1-2 Lacazette
2-2 Stindl

Germany grab an equaliser with just seconds remaining in the game, after it looked like France would secure the victory, after two goals from Alexandre Lacazette. Werner also netted for Germany who struggled to cope with the pace of Mbappe and Martial for large periods, but they could coming forward and it was the introduction of Gotze and Stindl who made the difference, linking up for the equalising goal.

Germany host France in an international friendly at the RheinEnergieStadion in Cologne on Tuesday, with the match featuring two of the likely favourites for the 2018 FIFA World Cup in Russia next summer.

Die Mannschaft are the World Cup holders, while Les Bleus were beaten finalists on home soil at UEFA Euro 2016. Both nations made easy work of qualification, finishing top of their respective groups. They are each in fine form, with neither having experienced defeat in their last six matches.

title: Disturbing moment distressed cow chases after 4WD carrying off her calves in a cage   1 NEWS NOW   T
tags: Disturbing moment|"distressed cow chases"|"after 4WD carrying off her calves"|"An emotional cow has been"|"filmed chasing her"|"Zealand road as they are transported"|"Animal-rights grop SAFE"|"Facebook this"|"concerned member"|"window to see what is happening."|"and appears to slow down."|"grieving mothers at hours old."|"are"|"killed"|"as"|"young"|"four"|"days"|"of"|"age."|"mother and her calves."
description:
An emotional cow has been filmed chasing her calves down a New Zealand road as they are transported on the back of a 4WD in a trailer.

Animal-rights grop SAFE posted the footage to Facebook this morning after it was sent to them by a concerned member of the public.
As the 4WD travels slowly, the mother cow can be seen running after her three calves while the driver appears to look out of his window to see what is happening. 

With their hazard lights flashing, the vehicle drives to the other side of the road and appears to slow down.
The person who sent us this clip told us the calves were in an enclosure with no cows for a couple of days afterwards, and then disappeared, a SAFE spokesperson told 7 News.
Like other mammals, a mother cow must give birth in order to produce milk. In the dairy industry calves are taken from their grieving mothers at hours old.
Some are kept as replacements for their mothers, or reared for meat, and in New Zealand, a shocking approximately two million are killed as young as four days of age.
The organisation said the video shows a strong bond between the mother and her calves.

tags: Germany|"vs"|"France"|"1-2"|"Highlights"|"Goals"|"14"|"November"|"2017"|"Germany vs France"|"Germany vs France 2017"|"Germany vs France 1-2"|"Germany France"|"Football"|"Minds"|"Lacazette"|"Deutschland"|"2x2"
description:
English Commentary
By FOOTBALL MINDS

Germany vs France 2-2 Highlights & Goals
14 November 2017.

0-1 Lacazette
1-1 Werner
1-2 Lacazette
2-2 Stindl

Germany grab an equaliser with just seconds remaining in the game, after it looked like France would secure the victory, after two goals from Alexandre Lacazette. Werner also netted for Germany who struggled to cope with the pace of Mbappe and Martial for large periods, but they could coming forward and it was the introduction of Gotze and Stindl who made the difference, linking up for the equalising goal.

Germany host France in an international friendly at the RheinEnergieStadion in Cologne on Tuesday, with the match featuring two of the likely favourites for the 2018 FIFA World Cup in Russia next summer.

Die Mannschaft are the World Cup holders, while Les Bleus were beaten finalists on home soil at UEFA Euro 2016. Both nations made easy work of qualification, finishing top of their respective groups. They are each in fine form, with neither having experienced defeat in their last six matches.

Je veux bien s√ªr parler du SLIME la star du web. Il existe mille fa√ßons d'en faire avec de l'eau sans eau ou m√™me avec de la lessive et apr√®s quelques recherches je pense que j'ai trouv√© une recette qui colle !  
Aujourd‚Äôhui on va faire du slime standard mais aussi un super slime !

Pour ma recette de slime il va vous falloir : un b√©cher de 250 ml, du borat de sodium aussi appel√© borax que l'on va trouver sous la forme de poudre ou de solutions pour les yeux. De colle blanche liquide √† base de PVA et de colorants alimentaires de la couleur que vous souhaitez histoire de s'en mettre plein la vue ! 

Alors pour ma recette de Slime on va commencer par prendre notre r√©cipient et y verser de la colle.
Si vous souhaitez colorer votre slime c'est maintenant qu'il faut le faire mais attention ne mettez pas trop de colorants √ßa peut casser l'effet et le rendre trop collant. 

Et maintenant vous prenez vos solutions pour les yeux.  
Et encore une fois on prend notre cuill√®re ou notre dos de fourchette et on touille ! Et l√† vous allez voir que la texture commence √† changer ! L√† on a du slime !!! 

Voici quelques pr√©cisions sur la r√©action : le pva est un polym√®re c'est √† dire une longue cha√Æne de mol√©cules on peut voir √ßa un petit peu comme des gens qui se tiennent par la main. Toutes ces mol√©cules vont s'accrocher au borax par liaison hydrog√®ne,  c'est ce qu'on appelle la r√©ticulation.
La cons√©quence de tout √ßa :  toutes ces cha√Ænes polym√®re vont s'associer entre elles et former un m√©lange bien solide et  vachement plus costaud.
Le slime contrairement √† l'eau est un liquide non newtonien.
Ce que √ßa veut dire c'est que la viscosit√© du liquide d√©pend de la force qu'on lui applique : en l'occurrence notre Slime est rh√©o√©paississant, c'est √† dire que plus on va essayer de l'√©tirer, plus on va lui appliquer de contraintes, plus sa viscosit√© va augmenter et plus il va √™tre r√©sistant.

Pour faire du Super slime XXL,  il vous faut donc un r√©cipient vachement plus grand et 3 litres de colle. 1 tonne 512 de borax. Beaucoup de mousse √† raser. Un wubble qui est une esp√®ce de gros ballon en fait mais bien √©lastique et un filet de badminton. 
On commence par verser la colle mais genre l√† c'est plus de la g√©n√©rosit√© hein‚Ä¶ puis la mousse √† raser.  
Vous l'aurez compris sur les quantit√©s on n'est pas √† plus ou moins 2L pr√®s.... Bon alors maintenant que vous avez votre m√©lange colle et mousse √† raser, et bien il faut touiller.

Et maintenant comme promis : la tonne 512 de borax !  
C'est parti : on r√©ticule tout notre m√©lange. Et puis on touille.  L√† √ßa commence √† devenir un peu plus ferme !
Oui l√† on a du SLIME XXL,  mais cette fois ci qui est un petit peu plus fluffy comme diraient les am√©ricains. Un petit  peu plus √©lastique encore !

Global megastar Dwayne Johnson headlines the action adventure ‚ÄúRampage,‚Äù directed by Brad Peyton.  

Primatologist Davis Okoye (Johnson), a man who keeps people at a distance, shares an unshakable bond with George, the extraordinarily intelligent, silverback gorilla who has been in his care since birth.  But a rogue genetic experiment gone awry mutates this gentle ape into a raging creature of enormous size.  To make matters worse, it‚Äôs soon discovered there are other similarly altered animals.  As these newly created alpha predators tear across North America, destroying everything in their path, Okoye teams with a discredited genetic engineer to secure an antidote, fighting his way through an ever-changing battlefield, not only to halt a global catastrophe but to save the fearsome creature that was once his friend.   

 ‚ÄúRampage‚Äù also stars Oscar nominee Naomie Harris (‚ÄúMoonlight‚Äù), Malin Akerman (TV‚Äôs ‚ÄúBillions‚Äù), Jake Lacy (TV‚Äôs ‚ÄúGirls‚Äù), Joe Manganiello (TV‚Äôs ‚ÄúTrue Blood‚Äù) and Jeffrey Dean Morgan (TV‚Äôs ‚ÄúThe Walking Dead‚Äù); as well as P.J. Byrne (‚ÄúThe Wolf of Wall Street‚Äù), Marley Shelton (‚ÄúSolace‚Äù), Breanne Hill (‚ÄúSan Andreas‚Äù), Jack Quaid (‚ÄúThe Hunger Games: Catching Fire‚Äù), and Matt Gerald (TV‚Äôs ‚ÄúDaredevil‚Äù). 

Peyton directs from a screenplay by Ryan Engle and Carlton Cuse & Ryan J. Condal and Adam Sztykiel, story by Ryan Engle, based on the video game Rampage. 

‚ÄúRampage is produced by Beau Flynn, John Rickard, Brad Peyton and Hiram Garcia.  It marks the third collaboration between Johnson, Peyton and Flynn, following the blockbuster hit ‚ÄúSan Andreas.‚Äù  Serving as executive producers are Marcus Viscidi, Dwayne Johnson, Dany Garcia, Jeff Fierson, Toby Emmerich, Richard Brener and Michael Disco, with Wendy Jacobson co-producing. 
The creative team includes production designer Barry Chusid (‚ÄúSan Andreas‚Äù), director of photography Jaron Presant (2nd unit, ‚ÄúStar Wars: The Last Jedi‚Äù), editor Jim May (‚ÄúGoosebumps‚Äù) and costume designer Melissa Bruning (‚ÄúDawn of the Planet of the Apes‚Äù).  Music will be composed by Andrew Lockington, who created the scores for ‚ÄúSan Andreas‚Äù and ‚ÄúJourney 2: The Mysterious Island.‚Äù
The ‚ÄúRampage‚Äù creatures are brought to life by acclaimed VFX supervisor Colin Strause (‚ÄúSan Andreas,‚Äù ‚ÄúX-Men: Apocalypse‚Äù), with five-time Academy Award-winning visual effects company Weta Digital (‚ÄúThe Lord of the Rings‚Äù Trilogy, ‚ÄúDawn of the Planet of the Apes‚Äù).

‚ÄúRampage‚Äù opens in theaters beginning April 20, 2018.
A New Line Cinema presentation, a Wrigley Pictures/Flynn Picture Company/7 Bucks Entertainment production, in association with ASAP Entertainment, ‚ÄúRampage‚Äù will be distributed by Warner Bros. Pictures, a Warner Bros. Entertainment Company.

description:
English Commentary
By FOOTBALL MINDS

Manchester United vs Newcastle 4-1 Highlights & Goals
18 November 2017.

0-1 Gayle
1-1 Anthony Martal
2-1 Smalling
3-1 Pogba
4-1 Lukaku

The quality of Manchester United shone through in the second half, after Newcastle started the game as the better of the two teams and took the lead early on through Gayle. However, United rallied and goals from Martial and Smalling saw them lead 2-1 at the break. The hosts were then terrific in the second half, straight from the off and goals from Pogba and Lukaku extended their lead and made it a comfortable victory, to move back into second position in the table.

3:15pm Saturday 18th November
Butarque   (Att: 11454)

Barcelona were not at their best at Butarque and Leganes had their chances, but LaLiga's leaders had enough in the tank to seal a 3-0 win.

Luis Suarez ended his Barcelona goal drought with a pair of scruffy goals as LaLiga's leaders escaped Leganes with a hard-earned 3-0 win.

Barca were nowhere near their fluent best, but ground out their 11th win from 12 games this term regardless.

Suarez broke his six-game goal drought with a scavenger's effort after an Ivan Cuellar error rendered a promising Leganes start redundant, and the hosts' goalkeeper was left helpless by a deflection as the Uruguay international struck again in the second half, with Paulinho tapping in a late consolation.

At the other end, Marc-Andre ter Stegen made a string of saves to preserve the comfortable nature of the scoreline, with half-time substitute Claudio Beauvue missing two fine Leganes openings.

Daunting trips to Juventus in the Champions League and second-placed Valencia next week now await Ernesto Valverde's side, although this victory ensures they will travel to Mestalla sure of keeping top spot.

tags: Atletico Madrid|"vs"|"Real Madrid"|"0-0"|"Highlights"|"Goals"|"18"|"November"|"2017"|"La Liga"|"Derby"|"Atletico Madrid vs Real Madrid"|"Atletico Madrid vs Real Madrid 0-0"|"Atletico Madrid vs Real Madrid 2017"|"Atletico Madrid vs Real Madrid all goals"|"Atletico Madrid vs Real Madrid highlights"|"Atletico Madrid Highlights"|"Real Madrid Highlights"|"Atletico vs Real"|"Atletico vs Real 0-0"|"Real Madrid vs Atletico 0-0"|"Griezmann"|"Cristiano Ronaldo"|"Benzema"|"Isco"|"Sergio Ramos"
description:
Atletico Madrid vs Real Madrid 0-0 - Extended Match Highlights - La Liga 18/11/2017 HD

Spanish La Liga
Atletico Madrid vs Real Madrid
7:45pm Saturday 18th November
Wanda Metropolitano   (Att: 66496)

Barcelona are now 10 points clear of Atletico Madrid and Real Madrid after the city rivals played out a drab draw on Saturday.

Atletico Madrid and Real Madrid have lost further ground on LaLiga leaders Barcelona this weekend after a lifeless 0-0 draw in the first derby to be played at the Wanda Metropolitano.

Barcelona cruised to a 3-0 win over Leganes earlier on Saturday and the subsequent derby stalemate means the Madrid sides are now 10 points behind Ernesto Valverde's high-flying Catalans.

The two teams, who sit fourth and third respectively, are also three points adrift of second-placed Valencia, who travel to Espanyol in their game in hand on Sunday.

Diego Simeone and Zinedine Zidane's sides have both fallen short of expectations so far this campaign and failure to win such a high-profile game will increase the strain on the two head coaches.

The best opportunity of the game came in just the third minute when Angel Correa clipped a shot wide after inadvertently being played in by Real Madrid defender Raphael Varane.

Karim Benzema and Cristiano Ronaldo struggled to make any significant inroads against Atletico's obdurate defence, which means the star forwards have now scored just two goals between them in a combined 16 league appearances this season. 

Atletico and Real Madrid know they must register wins against Levante and Malaga respectively next weekend if they are to get their stuttering league seasons back on track stand any chance of closing the significant gap to Barca.

title: Merkel : la patronne en danger ! #cdanslair 21.11.2017
description:
Apr√®s douze ans de pouvoir ininterrompu, Angela Merkel se retrouve dans l‚Äôincapacit√© de composer une coalition. Le couperet est tomb√© dimanche soir : Christian Lindner, chef de file des lib√©raux allemands, a claqu√© la porte des n√©gociations pour tenter de former une alliance gouvernementale in√©dite (CDU-CSU, FDP et Verts). Plongeant l‚ÄôAllemagne dans sa plus grosse crise politique depuis 1949 et la chanceli√®re allemande dans une situation tr√®s compliqu√©e.L‚Äô√©chec des n√©gociations pour former un gouvernement est en effet un camouflet pour Angela Merkel, vers qui tous les yeux se tournent depuis lundi. Affaiblie mais pas r√©sign√©e, la chanceli√®re a annonc√© hier qu‚Äôelle √©tait pr√™te √† √™tre de nouveau candidate en cas d‚Äô√©lections l√©gislatives anticip√©es. Mais outre-Rhin, les questions pleuvent depuis vingt-quatre heures : Comment sortir de la crise politique ? La doyenne de l'Europe n'est-elle pas fatigu√©e, us√©e pour mener cette bataille ? Peut-elle continuer √† gouverner malgr√© tout ? Est-ce la fin de l‚Äô√®re Merkel ?Le pr√©sident de la R√©publique f√©d√©rale, Frank-Walter Steinmeier, qui a d√©sormais la main dans cette crise en vertu de la Constitution, a annonc√© son intention de faire le tour des partis susceptibles de participer √† un gouvernement sous l‚Äô√©gide de la chanceli√®re : tous sauf l‚Äôextr√™me droite et la gauche radicale. Apr√®s un long entretien hier avec Angela Merkel, il a rencontr√© dans la journ√©e les dirigeants des Verts, avant mercredi une entrevue tr√®s attendue avec le pr√©sident de sa propre formation, le Parti social-d√©mocrate (SPD), qui jusqu‚Äôici refuse de s‚Äôallier √† la chanceli√®re. Objectif: tenter de trouver une solution pour √©viter que les Allemands n‚Äôaient √† retourner aux urnes, alors qu‚Äôils viennent d‚Äô√©lire leurs d√©put√©s.Une perspective qui plonge l‚ÄôUnion europ√©enne, d√©j√† affaiblie par le Brexit, encore un peu plus dans l‚Äôincertitude. L‚Äôinqui√©tude est d‚Äôautant plus palpable que l‚ÄôAllemagne a d√©j√† v√©cu un s√©isme politique lors des l√©gislatives du 24 septembre dernier avec l‚Äôentr√©e fracassante de d√©put√©s d‚Äôextr√™me droite √† la chambre des d√©put√©s, le Bundestag. La mont√©e de l‚ÄôAlternative pour l‚ÄôAllemagne (AfD) pourrait se confirmer, voire prendre de l‚Äôampleur en cas d‚Äô√©lections anticip√©es, au vu des sondages.Un scrutin qui pourrait √©galement sonner le glas de la longue carri√®re politique de la ¬´ femme la plus puissante du monde ¬ª (selon le classement Forbes), qui, il n'y a pas si longtemps, semblait invincible dans son propre pays. D‚Äôapr√®s une derni√®re enqu√™te publi√©e dans le journal Die Welt, 61 % des Allemands souhaitent que la chanceli√®re se retire si les n√©gociations de coalition √©chouent.

description:
Dortmund vs Tottenham 1-2 ‚óè All Goals & Highlights HD ‚óè 21 Nov 2017 - Champions League
Click Here For More Highlights And Goals! - https://goo.gl/Renzrd

Harry Kane and Son Heung-min scored as Tottenham came from behind to beat Borussia Dortmund 2-1 in the Champions League.

Tottenham came from behind to beat Borussia Dortmund 2-1 and make certain of their status as Champions League Group H winners.
Second-placed Real Madrid can match Tottenham's points tally on the final matchday of the group stages but Mauricio Pochettino's men will remain in first place regardless thanks to their superior head-to-head record over the holders, giving them hope of a favourable draw in the last 16.
Meanwhile, the results ended Dortmund's chances of qualifying for the knockout stages.

Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang marked his return to the Dortmund side following a club-enforced one-match suspension for disciplinary reasons by scoring the opening goal, as Peter Bosz's side sought to relieve the pressure building on the coach.
But Spurs have relished Champions League fixtures this season and they played with their usual composure and patience at Signal Iduna Park, where Dele Alli set up Harry Kane to score the equaliser after 49 minutes and Son Heung-Min completed the comeback by netting the winner with just 14 minutes left to play.
Dortmund started the game brightly and Andriy Yarmolenko combined with Mario Gotze to create a shooting chance after 12 minutes but his effort from the edge of the penalty area flew tamely into the arms of Hugo Lloris.
Yarmolenko chipped a weighted pass over the Tottenham defence for Aubameyang six minutes later, but the Gabonese striker side-footed his shot wide to the right of the net with only Lloris to beat.
Son Heung-min almost connected with a Jan Vertonghen free-kick just before the half-hour mark, but he was denied by Roman Burki and one minute later Dortmund were ahead.
Raphael Guerreiro's pass was brilliantly flicked into the box by Yarmolenko and Aubameyang raced after it before driving the ball low into the left corner of the net.

Mais de quoi est-il vraiment question ? Pourquoi cette forme d‚Äô√©criture d√©cha√Æne-t-elle les passions depuis des mois en France ? En 2015, le Haut conseil √† l'√©galit√© entre les femmes et les hommes (qui d√©pend du Premier ministre) avait publi√© un guide incitant les pouvoirs publics √† adopter une communication sans st√©r√©otypes de sexe. Dans cet ouvrage scolaire, les diff√©rents m√©tiers que peuvent exercer les hommes et les femmes sont ainsi orthographi√©s : agriculteur¬∑rice¬∑s, artisan¬∑e¬∑s ou encore commer√ßant¬∑e¬∑s. L‚Äôid√©e est de faire en sorte que le masculin ne l‚Äôemporte plus sur le f√©minin au pluriel, mais que les deux sexes soient mis sur le m√™me pied d‚Äô√©galit√©. Afin de mettre un terme √† la hi√©rarchisation des sexes.Mais cette nouvelle approche de l‚Äôorthographe n'est pas du go√ªt de tous, et certainement pas de l'Acad√©mie fran√ßaise. Les Immortels ont pouss√© un  cri d‚Äôalarme le 26 octobre dernier, d√©non√ßant un p√©ril mortel pour la langue fran√ßaise. Le philosophe Rapha√´l Enthoven y voit, pour sa part, une agression de la langue par l‚Äô√©galitarisme, et plusieurs d√©put√©s Les R√©publicains ont envoy√© une lettre au minist√®re de l‚ÄôEducation pour demander l‚Äôinterdiction de l‚Äô√©criture inclusive dans les manuels scolaires.Plusieurs partisans de la r√©forme sont √©galement mont√©s au cr√©neau. Ainsi l‚Äôancienne ministre des Droits des femmes Laurence Rossignol a affirm√© ce mercredi que ce n‚Äô√©tait pas le r√¥le du Premier ministre de statuer sur ce point. La Ville de Paris a √©galement d√©clar√© aujourd‚Äôhui qu‚Äôelle la garderait tout de m√™me. Par ailleurs, pr√®s de 300 professeurs d‚Äô√©coles, coll√®ges et lyc√©es ont fait savoir dans une tribune publi√©e par Slate.fr il y a quinze jours qu‚Äôils avaient d√©cid√© d'adopter cette √©criture.Si le d√©bat fait rage en France, en Belgique et au Qu√©bec, le concept d‚Äô√©criture inclusive fait √©galement son chemin, plus discr√®tement, les pol√©miques en moins.

description:
ATLETICO MADRID vs AS ROMA 2-0 ‚óè All Goals & Highlights HD ‚óè 22 Nov 2017 - CHAMPIONS LEAGUE
Click Here For More Highlights And Goals! - https://goo.gl/Renzrd

Qualifying for the knockout rounds remains a slim hope for Atletico Madrid, but Antoine Griezmann's wonderful goal boosted their chances.
Antoine Griezmann kept Atletico Madrid's slight hopes of Champions League qualification alive with a sensational scissor-kick volley and a sublime assist to down 10-man Roma 2-0 on Wednesday.
The Atleti talisman had not scored in his last eight matches in all competitions, but broke the deadlock in style at the Wanda Metropolitano to keep Atletico in the competition.
Substitute Angel Correa performed miracles to keep the ball in at the byline, his cross hung up for Griezmann to launch himself into an unstoppable flying volley.
Roma, who headed to the Spanish capital on the back of six straight wins in all competitions, knew a draw would send them through to the knockout rounds and set up cautiously as a result.
It was therefore always likely to require something brilliant to break Roma down and Griezmann's magical impact provided the spark Atleti needed, the striker then sliding Kevin Gameiro through to double the lead after defender Bruno Peres saw red.
Atletico have to win at already qualified Chelsea on matchday six to have any hope of qualifying, with Roma still in pole position ahead of their clash with Group C whipping boys Qarabag.
